+------ [Core serveR] Installer -------+
| Date: 2007-10-13                     |
| Author: evrim@core.gen.tr            |
| Web: http://www.core.gen.tr/         |
+--------------------------------------+

+ REQUIREMENTS
+User Server
 + darcs
 + svn
 + cvs
 + wget
 + tar
 + mv
 + rm 
 + ln
 + find
 + chmod
 + chown
 + screen
 + su
+System Server
 + sudo
 + apache2
 + apache2ctl
 + useradd
 + groupadd
 + apxs2

See UBUNTU file or http://www.core.gen.tr/projects/core-server/doc/UBUNTU 
for specific questions.

+User Installation
After you met requirements, do
  sh ./install.sh ~/core-server/

This would install core-server to your home 
directory. 

+System Wise Installation
After you met requirements, do
  sh ./install.sh /home/core/core-server/

This would install core-server to a user
named core's home directory.
